snippet.textDisplay: The Baul's of Bengal are Pir's or Fakirs. Heavily influenced by Bhatiyali , which are sons of Majhi's and also from Hindu Kirtan and Sufi. Baul songs often speak of Krishna and in the same breath will speak of Khwaja and Allah. So its pretty difficult to put a finger on specifics in this genre. Is one big original melting pot of fusion. The best way to understand Baul, is simply enjoy it!
